      <textAnnotation id="sid-12388869-7126-4EE2-A729-D3752A13E4DD" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Internal Sales - Automatic
External Sales - Manual upload using utility solution same as IF</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-01B5A99B-95BF-4D05-8362-E7A789DDCCFB" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>For internal sales PR will be created automatically</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5F58A9F3-5C4F-433A-A366-288C07A93195" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>When customer PO is received via EDI, sales order confirmation will be sent to customer automatically back via EDI (per schedule batch job time)
 
When customer PO is received via non-EDI, then sales order confirmation will be sent to customer via email. </text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
